---
title: Texan-Style BBQ Pulled Chicken Roll with Creamy Slaw & Potato Fries
description: Saddle up and get ready for our new favourite sandwich combo! Pulled chicken, creamy slaw and barbecue sauce all come
together in a toasted brioche bun for a handheld meal that packs a punch. All you need is a side of fries to make this dish
complete.
